result.name: biological-data-on-individual-whelks-buccinum-undatum-to-determine-population-dynamics-in-uk-wa
result.notes:
Measurements of height, width, weight, shell weight, body weight, sex 
maturity, age and Fulton factor for 383 individual whelk (*Buccinum undatum*), 
caught in 2018 and 2015 In UK waters (North Norfolk, Poole, Portsmouth, Celtic 
Sea).
